name: Vanguard U.S. Total Market Index ETF (CAD-hedged)
longDescription: The investment objective of Vanguard U.S. Total Market Index ETF CAD-hedged the ETF is to track, to the extent reasonably possible and before fees and expenses, the performance of the CRSP US Total Market Index CAD-hedged the Index. To achieve its investment objective, the ETF employs a passive management, or indexing, investment approach designed to track the performance of the Index by investing primarily in a U.S. domiciled fund managed by The Vanguard Group, Inc. U.S. domiciled Vanguard Fund, that seeks to track the CRSP US Total Market Index.
